(167, 'Micon Pneu AG', 'frei@miconpneu.ch', 'open invoices', 'Good morning\r\n\r\nThe following invoices are still outstanding:\r\n\r\nR 165523\r\nCHF 4382.76\r\n\r\nR167090\r\nCHF 1870.26\r\n\r\nR166261\r\nCHF 3312.75\r\n\r\nPlease pay immediately.\r\n\r\nMicon Pneu AG\r\n', '2025-12-01 07:28:05'),
(168, 'Margaret Parisi', 'msplincoln@hotmail.com', 'Car Rental', 'Hello, I have been trying to reserve a car online. We arrive 8:20 pm Bandaranaike Airport on Dec. 24 and leave 8:00 am Dec. 31 from same. We can pick up and return the car wherever convenient for you. Please let us know if you have a car available for this time. Thank you!', '2025-12-02 00:13:49'),
(169, 'Vaclav Homolka', 'homolka.vaclav@seznam.cz', 'Third party Liability', 'Hello, I am going to make reservation for car, but what is the limit of cover for third party liability?  The maximum amount? Thanks in advance, Vaclav ', '2025-12-06 19:52:31'),
(170, 'Mauricio Contreras', 'mauricio@contreras.se', 'quote', 'Hi, \r\nI just wanted a quote but to see the price I hade to go trough the whole process. ca you please cancel the reservation? I just made? You see my name and email above. In the future, to avoide this kind of situation i would be best if your website listed the prices. Please confirm the cancellation.\r\nKind regards,\r\nMauricio', '2025-12-07 09:38:34'),
(171, 'Yeolan ', 'yeolan_nikhil@hotmail.com', 'Rent a car 26th december to 03rd January ', 'Hi there, \r\n\r\nI need to rent a car 26th December, 13:00 up to 03rd January, 20:00 pm. \r\nplease let me know costs and also how to obtain a TDL. \r\n\r\nThank you, \r\nYeolan', '2025-12-09 03:22:36'),
(172, 'RAJA PRIYATHAM VARMA PENUMATSA', 'penumatsa2997@gmail.com', 'cancellation of the booking', 'i wanted to check the price of the total booking which accidentally made a booking of the car', '2025-12-13 06:25:37'),
(173, 'chamara ', 'chamara.iu@gmail.com', 'Requesting a rough estiamte', 'Hi I am planning a trip to sri lanka in oct 2026.\r\nmay i know the monthly rate for a small car ( Honda Grace / prius ) or even fit would be ok . i would also need ne baby car seat  and toddler car eat ( 4 year old)', '2025-12-13 19:14:51'),
(174, 'karan', 'singh.karan118@gmail.com', 'Car rental with Driver', 'Looking for car rental from 18-12-2025 to 27-12-2025, for 6 people, please send me a quote. ', '2025-12-14 06:59:48'),
(175, 'Robert King', 'wormarse@gmaill.com', 'car hire', 'Hi how much for 13 days car hire  without driver from 1st feb 2026 please', '2025-12-15 15:28:24'),
(176, 'ricardo ', 'rsemeles@gmail.com', 'rent a car', 'I’m looking to rent a car from August 7 to August 21, 2026. We are a family of four, so a Honda Grace or a similar vehicle would be suitable.\r\n\r\nBefore proceeding, I’d appreciate your help with a few questions:\r\n• Do you offer full insurance coverage?\r\n• What is the booking process?\r\n• How is the payment process?\r\n• What is your cancellation policy?\r\n• Is it possible to return the vehicle in Trincomalee instead of Colombo?\r\n• How is the process to aquire a sri lanka drivers licence?\r\n\r\nThank you in advance, and I look forward to your reply.\r\n\r\nRicardo Semeles', '2025-12-17 14:36:59'),
(177, 'Sampath Wickramasinghe', 'sampath65a@gmail.com', 'Self Drive Car Hire', 'Hello...\r\n\r\nI am looking to hire a standard automatic car with A/C from 19th to 23rd March 2026, with  a possibility to extend till 28th March.\r\n\r\nCan you please provide me a quotation with all the details.\r\n\r\nKind Regards,\r\n\r\nSampath', '2025-12-19 13:38:44'),
(178, 'Devijs Zivers', 'devijs@abtechnology.lv', 'TDL', 'Dear Madam or Sir, I have ordered car rent from your company through EconomyCarRentals. e-Voucher No is EC3E4E58, car rental provider confirmation no is 4455. Could you pleas help me to get Temporary Driving License? Kind regards, Devijs', '2025-12-22 09:42:08'),
(179, 'Marek Zieliński', 'mwzieli@gmail.com', 'Rent a car', 'Do you have any cars for rent from 29.12.2025 -11.01.2026\r\nRegards,\r\nMarek Z.', '2025-12-23 10:34:03'),
(180, 'P B Fink', 'fil64fil64@gmail.com', ' drivers licence Sri Lanka ', 'Dear Sir/madam,\n\nI will be arriving  in Sri Lanka in January 2026 and have booked a car with your company. I have a Dutch drivers licence and was wondering if it is ok to drive in Sri Lanka with this licence.?\nThe booking has been made under the name  Judy Geusebroek\n\nkind regards,\n\nPhil Fink \n \n\n', '2025-12-24 10:31:29'),
(181, 'Gyula', 'dergyula@gmail.com', 'Car rental January', 'Hi,\nI would like to rent a car from the 8. of January and bringing back on the 13. of January.\nCan you pls send me a quotation for a Honda Insight or similar?\nAnothe question: I have a Hungarian driving license. Can you organize a TDL for me? I have no international driving license.\nThanks and best regards,\nGyula', '2025-12-26 11:25:14'),
(182, 'Darren Howland', 'Darren@alvio.co.uk', 'Sri Lankan Car Hire', 'Hi there, if book a hire car on your website with a copy of my IDP and my passport and UK driving license, does that give you enough time to apply for a Sri Lankan tourist license on my behalf before I arrive on the 29th December at 10:00am? ', '2025-12-26 22:42:38'),
(183, 'Darren Howland', 'Darren@alvio.co.uk', 'Sri Lankan Car Hire', 'Hi there, if I book a hire car through your website and upload my IDP, my passport and my UK driving license, does that give you enough time to apply for a Sri Lankan tourist driving license on my behalf before my arrival on the 29th December at 10:00am?', '2025-12-26 22:45:00'),
(184, 'Toby Eadie', 'toby.eadie@npltd.com', 'Car Rental', 'Can you please give me a price to hire a small car (sizuki swift) for 6 days from Colombo', '2025-12-28 19:13:53'),
(185, 'Maja Todorovic', 'hickok.maja@gmail.com', 'Pick up & Drop off locations', 'Hi, I was wondering is it possible to pick up the car at the Colombo International Airport, and drop it off at Kandy? We want to take a train from Kandy to Ella afterwards. \r\nWhen I go to the reservation page on your website, drop off location only offers one option, and I read somewhere that you have options for different pick up and drop off locations', '2025-12-29 08:25:04'),
(186, 'Maja Todorovic', 'hickok.maja@gmail.com', 'Pick up & Drop off locations', 'Hi, I was wondering is it possible to pick up the car at the Colombo International Airport, and drop it off at Kandy? We want to take a train from Kandy to Ella afterwards. \r\nWhen I go to the reservation page on your website, drop off location only offers one option, and I read somewhere that you have options for different pick up and drop off locations', '2025-12-29 08:25:06'),
(187, 'Raymond Abbott', 'raymond.abbott@jmailservice.com', 'Top of Google - Without the Hassle', 'We help businesses get seen online fast - usually within 24 hours. You choose the keywords, and we drive the right visitors straight to your site.\r\nCan I show you how it works?', '2025-12-31 03:31:03'),
(188, 'marlon anthony vanderwall', 'marlonvanderwall@gmail.com', 'rent a small  car ', 'Good morning     can you please send me a quote . small car  automatic .   unlimited mileage . sri lanka licence .  pick up airport 03 february 2026 return 07 february 2026 .  full insurance  100%  cover  no liability . age 70 .  valid licences in hand , srilankan ,switzerland , australian , international .\r\narrival edelweiss airlines  colombo 03 february  10,15  am \r\nthank you for your help \r\nRegards\r\nmarlon vanderwall ', '2026-01-02 11:31:49'),
(189, 'Tijmen', 'tijmen@f12development.nl', 'drivers license', 'I have booked a car with you on the 22nd of January. Can you arrange the required drivers license for me? What are the costs?', '2026-01-04 13:08:26'),
(190, 'Polina', 'polina.bielova@gmail.com', 'Car rent', 'Hello! Is it possible rent car, automaat from 7 until 9.01?  ', '2026-01-05 08:23:22'),
(191, 'Vivek', 'n.vivekananda@gmail.com', 'Looking to rent a car', 'Hi, I am writing from Singapore. I am looking to rent a car for self-drive for one week from 17 to 23 January 2026. I am looking in the category of Nissan X Trail or equivalent. Can you give me some options and cost? Are you able to drop off the car at Hilton Colombo Residences? Please let me know. Thank you.\r\n\r\nMy mobile number (also Whatsapp) is +6597709715. Thank you. Vivek\r\n', '2026-01-05 15:20:49'),
(192, 'Vince ', 'vince_2345@hotmail.com', 'Car Rental ', 'Hi, \n\nI would like to enquire how much it costs to rent a Suzuki Swift from March 11 - March 20. Pick up and Drop off from Colombo ', '2026-01-06 05:15:34'),
(193, 'Maciej Kocon', 'maciejjan.kocon@edhec.com', 'Rental 17-30 Jan Colombo Intl Airport', 'Hello, \r\nI want to rent a car for the period starting 17 January (12:00 PM, Colombo Airport) and ending  30 January (4:00 PM, also Colombo Airport). \r\nThe car will be used by 2 adults and 1 5 y/o child to travel to Arugam Bay for vacation.  I will be the primary driver (47 y/o, citizen of Poland (EU), holder of International Driving Permit). \r\nCan you pls make me an offer for a car suitable for 3 people for the period mentioned? \r\nAlso, will you be able to arrange for me the Sri Lankan driving permit prior to renting the car? \r\nThanks in advance!\r\nMaciek', '2026-01-06 17:12:26'),
(194, 'Ivo Nano', 'ivo@aasageko.eu', 'Car for rent 21.Feb - 8.March', 'Hello,\nDo you have a small and cheap car to rent between February 21st and March 8th? \nWe are 3 passengers.', '2026-01-07 07:15:48'),
(195, 'Vaclav Homolka', 'homolka.vaclav@seznam.cz', 'reservation form does not work', 'I try to make a reservation for Toyota Aqua 21.2 to 07.03 2026, and the form is not workin. I fill al the Items but it is not possible to submit. Thanks, Vaclav, Czech republic ', '2026-01-07 19:38:38'),
(196, 'Jan Stepan', 'hking@seznam.cz', 'License', 'Hello, I have a car booked with you through CarFlexi. The reservation number is CFD44F4C. I read in the terms and conditions that I will need to be authorized by the Sri Lankan Automobile Association. Could you please write to me what I need to do to get this license? If you can arrange it for me, please write to me what you need for it and where I should send it. Thank you. Sincerely, Jan Stepan.', '2026-01-09 13:47:40'),
(197, 'Waldemar Pakizer', 'takipaki@wp.pl', 'Car and  Sri Lanka driving Permit', 'Will arrive to Sri Lanka on 18 of January. Would like to rent a car till 31 of January , will also need Sri Lanka driving permit. Can you organize both?\r\n\r\nkind regards\r\n\r\nWaldemar Pakizer', '2026-01-09 16:04:25'),
(198, 'Ryan ', 'rynewtsy@icloud.com', 'Car rental', 'Hi there,\r\nI’m looking to rent a car for an up coming vacation.\r\nPick up date would be Sunday 5th April at approx 10am.\r\nReturn date would be Thursday 16th April at approx 1:30pm.\r\nWe are staying in Negombo (Kurana) so any office that is closest to this please. \r\nWe are looking at a vehicle to accommodate 2 adults and 2 children (1 child would require a child seat 3yrs of age). \r\nCould you kindly give me a quote please. \r\nRegards\r\nMr Newton.', '2026-01-09 23:31:55'),
(199, 'Dimuthu Liyanage', 'taprobane@yahoo.co.nz', 'Car Hire', 'Hi team looking for car rental from tomorrow 12th to 26th  January. Plz contact me on 0707569140. Drop off at Airport on 26th.\r\nDimuthu ', '2026-01-11 14:14:43'),
(200, 'Pruthviraj ', 'pruthvi.psm@gmail.com', 'Self Drive car + Temp Drive Permit Quatation', 'Hi Team, I am travelling to Srilanka for a week and reaching there by evening of 15th Feb, i need a SELF drive car from 16th Feb morning till 21st Feb evning(6 days).\r\nI am planning to get quatation for TOYOTA YARIS or AQUA, need in AUTOMATIC transmission. Including quatation for arranging TDP (Temparory Driving Permit).', '2026-01-12 11:29:11'),
(201, 'Andrew grant', 'iamandygrant@googlemail.com', 'Car hire ', 'I have a car booked with you for January 25th for one day. Booking reference LK908268330. Confirmation ACR/2026/01/90.  \r\n\r\nPlease let me know how I inform you which hotel I am staying at?\r\n\r\nPlease advise what charge if any you apply for a 67 year old driver?\r\n\r\nThanks \r\nAndy ', '2026-01-12 13:02:57'),
(202, 'Viktoria Kyšová', 'viktoria.kysova@gmail.com', 'scooter rental', 'Hello, my name is Viktoria and I want to visit your country from 19.2 to 1.3. 2026 with my frieds. My friends have rented a car from you on this date. My husband and I would like to rent 2 scooters. My question is, do you also rent scooters or can you recommend a scooter rental near you for getting along with my friends? Thank you for your early response.  With regards    Viktoria.', '2026-01-13 20:08:59'),
(203, 'Lenka Šefrnová', 'sefrnova.lenka@gmail.com', 'Rent a car', 'Hello, \r\n\r\nI would like 4x4 car from 11.-22.6.2026. Pick up in Colombo. How much cost? Without shofer.', '2026-01-14 09:38:31'),
(204, 'Asela', 'aselamalshan5@gmail.com', 'Rental for Aqua', 'I need Aqua car from 26jan to 03rd feb please provide me rental and charge for additional KM', '2026-01-14 16:37:04'),
(205, 'Roman Hromnik', 'office@bsn.sk', 'Car rental', 'Hello,\nWe have rented a car from your company through economybookings.com platform\nReservation number for SR Rent a Car : BGP/2026/02/51\nAs we will need a local driving license, I would like to ask you, if you can arrange that for us.\n\nThank you.\n\nRoman', '2026-01-14 19:45:19'),
(206, 'Santosh Patil', 'santosh3332@gmail.com', 'Need car with Chauffer from 6 to 15th Feb pickup and drop at Colombo Airport', 'Please contact or whats app on 8806707974 ', '2026-01-15 07:36:14'),
(207, 'santiago', 'rakbcn888@gmail.com', 'D012707704-RRTP', 'Good morning,\r\nI have a reservation with you made through Discovercars: D012707704-RRTP.\r\nI am a driver from Spain, I have an international driving permit, and I would like to know what documents I need to send you in order to rent the car on February 26th.\r\n\r\nI look forward to hearing from you.\r\nBest regards,\r\nSantiago', '2026-01-21 16:54:17'),
(208, 'Edwin Duncan', 'ed@elodi.net', 'Hello + Feb Booking with you', 'Hello!\r\nI have booked via economy car rentals under reference : EC9487F4\r\nI will have my UK license and IDP1949 but I think we need to have it authenticated by AAC office in Colombo. I understand that I can do that on arrival at Bandaranaike International Airport (BIA) — the service is available to tourists with a valid IDP, processed right in the arrivals area and usually ready within minutes. Is this correct?  \r\nMany thanks!\r\nEdwin Duncan', '2026-01-22 13:54:22'),
(209, 'SHUNSUKE SHIRATO', 'shibuya_20cents@yahoo.co.jp', 'Inquiry', 'I would like to rent a car for one week starting from May 2, but I would like to check the price before making a reservation. Since the input form is only for booking and does not show the price, could you provide me with the price if I share the details with you?', '2026-01-23 02:48:56'),
(210, 'Shanthan Navaratnam', 'snshanthan@gmail.com', 'Query for a month renta', 'Hi,\r\nI am a Norwegian citizen, want to rent a car in colombo.\r\nI will have a Sri lankan driving license but most of the time use an experienced Sinhalese driver. Want to rent a car or van from the 16th of February to  the 9th of March. Want to know the availability of a car similar to Toyota Axio 165 (hybrid) or a van similar to Mitsubishi L300 or a smaller KDH. Me and my family only will be the passengers. Please give me the price for a month, how many km the vehicle already has done, with AC and Auto(gear). I am 59 and used to car rental in europe and the north America.  Thank you and hope for a quick response. Regs. Shanthan  ', '2026-01-23 11:54:51'),
(211, 'miles r ashworth', 'destinationdartmoor@outlook.com', 'Car Rental prices', 'We arrive in columbo airport ( sri lanka) on the 28th Feb  2026@11:00 and eave at 16:00 on 8th March. Please can you provide quotes for the different types of cars you have available. Kind regards\r\n\r\nMiles Ashworth', '2026-01-24 14:01:29'),
(212, 'Thomas Poggensee', 'tpoggensee@gmx.de', 'Rent a economy car ', 'Hello \r\nI want to rent a Suzuki swift or Toyota Vitz or something in this size from 14.2.2026 until 6.3.2026 .\r\nI am 67 years old. I need a normal CDW. \r\nAnd  I need a Sri Lanka driver license. \r\nRegards Thomas ', '2026-01-25 12:58:53'),
(213, 'Robert LAMBERTZ', 'robert.lambertz@live.ca', 'Rent a car without driver', 'Hello,\r\nI will be traveling to Sri Lanka with my two children from April 11 to April 26, 2026. I would like to rent a car. I would like to know the price for an SUV and for a smaller car such as a Toyota, depending on the cost.\r\n\r\nI do not have a Sri Lankan driver’s license, but I do have my Canadian driver’s license as well as an International Driving Permit.\r\n\r\nTherefore, we will need one Sri Lankan driving license for me and one Sri Lankan driving license for one of my children.\r\n\r\nI am 66 years old, and my children are 38 and 41 years old. Would it be possible to provide me with a price including full insurance coverage?\r\n\r\nThank you very much for your kindness.\r\n\r\n\r\n', '2026-01-28 00:40:43'),
(214, 'Olive', 'oliverdon@hotmail.co.uk', 'Rent a car self driving', 'Please send a quote for a car from 24 /02/2026 to 30/03/2026, rent a car. SUV category vehicle.', '2026-01-31 12:33:37'),
(215, 'Louis Curtil', 'louis.curtil@gmail.Com', 'Hire car', 'Hi,\n\nI’m looking to hire a car for our trip to Sri Lanka from 22 March 2026 to 17 April 2026. We would like an SUV, as we are 2 adults and one baby.\n\nI have a few questions:\n\nDo you provide baby seats, or should we bring our own on the plane?\n\nWhat are the driver’s license requirements for driving in Sri Lanka?\n\nCould you explain the total price including the different insurances?\n\nDo you have rates for a one-month rental?\n\nWhen I read about driving in Sri Lanka online, I see mixed opinions about safety. Could you enlighten me on this? I would like the freedom to go where I want when I want, but I’m also open to the option of hiring a driver.\n\nThanks,\n\nLouis', '2026-02-01 10:09:05'),
(216, 'jaime falcao', 'jaime.a.falcao@gmail.com', 'quote for renting a car', 'Hi \r\nI would like to have a quote to rent a car from 10 feb 2026 (16:30) to 3  marc 2026 (10.00)  unlimited millage . I will driving around sri lanka tourist routes.\r\n\r\nWe are a couple from Portugal  - 64 years old. I need a medium size confortable car for two people with a trunk that can take two 25 kg suitcases . we like cars that are high if possivel. I am very used in driving renting cars\r\n\r\nplease send me a quote with full insurance for the car to my mail : jaime.a.falcao@gmail.com\r\n\r\nthanks\r\n\r\njaime falcao', '2026-02-02 02:44:32'),
(217, 'Mr James Keith Finney', 'james@international-tool.com', 'Booking with Holiday Autos LK9229999290 ', 'please help me, i have emailed many times about credit card name and sri lankan driving permit. Please reply. thanks James ', '2026-02-02 11:31:21');
