    </div>\r\n            <h5>Navigating a Vehicle Accident in Sri Lanka</h5>\r\n            <p>Driving in a foreign country can be exciting, but preparation is essential for unexpected situations like accidents...</p>\r\n            <a href=\"[[~7]]\" class=\"read-btn\">Read Article →</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4\">\r\n        <div class=\"blog-card p-0\">\r\n          <div class=\"blog-img\">\r\n            <img src=\"assets/images/blog/road_sign.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"blog-content\">\r\n            <div class=\"blog-meta\">\r\n              <span><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Travel Guide</span>\r\n              <span><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i> Oct 27, 2021</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3>Essential Guide to Sri Lanka’s Traffic Rules for Drivers</h3>\r\n            <p>Planning to explore Sri Lanka at your own pace? Renting a car is ideal—especially for hidden gems—but knowing the local traffic rules is essential.</p>\r\n            <a href=\"[[~13]]\" class=\"read-btn\">Read Article →</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4\">\r\n        <div class=\"blog-card p-0\">\r\n          <div class=\"blog-img\">\r\n            <img src=\"assets/images/blog/drive_road.jpg\" alt=\"\">\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"blog-content\">\r\n            <div class=\"blog-meta\">\r\n              <span><i class=\"fas fa-user\"></i>Travel Guide</span>\r\n              <span><i class=\"far fa-clock\"></i> April 19, 2024</span>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <h3>How to travel in Sri Lanka at your own pace?</h3>\r\n            <p>Plan how you’ll get around Sri Lanka. If you like traveling freely at your own pace, you have several options.</p>\r\n            <a href=\"[[~14]]\" class=\"read-btn\">Read Article →</a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>