(2078, 'Oleksandr Sennik', 'sennik.a.sennik@gmail.com', '+48', '696262645', 'rent-a-car', 'Colombo Bandaranaike International Airport (CMB), Airport and Aviation Services (Sri Lanka) (Private) Limited, Canada Friendship Rd, Катунейейк, Шрі-Ланка', '2026-01-03 15:00:00', 'SR Rent A Car Sri Lanka, Negombo - Colombo Main Road, Seeduwa, Шрі-Ланка', '2026-01-25 18:00:00', '150 KM', 'No', 'No', '', '', '', 'Hi there!\r\n\r\nMy family and I will arrive at Bandaranaike International Airport on January 3, 2026, at 13:55, so we’ll need a car around 15:00. There will be 5 of us (4 adults and a 6-year-old child), one suitcase, and a few backpacks.\r\nThe return date is planned for January 25, 2026, at your Colombo office.\r\n\r\nWill you have a free car for the period I indicated?\r\nWhat are the possible options for cars and their cost?\r\nIs it possible to add two drivers to the rental agreement?\r\nTo explain: I’ll be driving the car from January 3 to January 20, then I’ll be flying home. From January 20 to January 25, my father-in-law (who is traveling with us) would drive the car. So I’m wondering if we can list both of us as drivers from the start, to avoid coming back for a re-registration.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to your reply.\r\nThank you,\r\nOleksandr', 'car_015', '[\"Booster Seat\"]', 0, 0, 0, 0, 110, 811, 921, 'MjA3OA%3D%3D', '5', '2025-10-30 21:21:09', 'G9508'),
